data.description: Why wait to build when you can own this beautiful MOVE IN READY, 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom home with a living room on each floor and a fully fenced yard. The location of this home is in a great, growing area; PERFECT for families with top-rated schools, including a new elementary school right down the street. This home is also convenient to shopping and not far from the St. Johns River and everything it has to offer. This home has an abundance of space for your family to flourish and grow both inside and out; it also has a screen for the garage door to provide even more space! Don't miss out on the chance to make this beautiful home yours today!
